###  http://metadata.un.org/sdg/C120801
<http://metadata.un.org/sdg/C120801> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                              <http://metadata.un.org/sdg/ontology#Indicator> ,
                                              skos:Concept ;
                                     <http://metadata.un.org/sdg/ontology#isIndicatorOf> <http://metadata.un.org/sdg/12.8> ;
