###  https://conservationstandards.org/library-item/actions-classification#10.4
<https://conservationstandards.org/library-item/actions-classification#10.4> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                                                                      skos:Concept ;
                                                                             skos:broader <https://conservationstandards.org/library-item/actions-classification#10> ;
